run the scripts/data_downloader.py to download the dataset.

cd frontend
npm run dev


from the root directory, for the backend
uvicorn app.backend.main:app --reload


python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m uvicorn app.backend.main:app --reload


Use this command to run the evaluation
OLLAMA_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_SEC=900 python scripts/run_benchmarks.py --run-id <output_name> --outdir comparison_runs/multi_bias_runs --datasets retail_kaggle --tasks <id from the registry. ex: retail/05> --pipelines single,multi --with-judge --task-timeout-sec 1800